label: Registry Integrity & Zero-Point
mathematical_goal: Verify that all 125 geometric residues are properly mapped and zero-point energy is exactly zero
theoretical_significance: The Registry Integrity certificate ensures that all 125 physical parameters derived from the G2 manifold are properly mapped to geometric residues. The zero-point check verifies that vacuum energy is exactly zero at the geometric level, with the observed cosmological constant arising from dynamical symmetry breaking, not from a bare vacuum term.
